The problem is the previous diagram is not the way it will play out.  White wasn't thinking about how Black should respond in a way that is best for Black.

In response to the cut, Black will play the maek at 2.  Even if White connects Black 4 takes away a vital liberty and \cf1\b White is dead due to a lack of liberties.\cf0\b0
